# Phase 8.2 — Encounter/Tactical Mode Review Document

**Date:** 2026-04-05 00:40
**Status:** Implemented Successfully

## Overview

Implemented Phase 8.2 Encounter/Tactical Mode from `rpg-design.txt`. This moves the RPG system from simple "scene + dialogue + choices" to structured encounter state with turn order, combat/social/standoff encounters, actor stats, player actions, NPC tactical actions, encounter log, and bounded state transitions.

