## Design Rules Compliance

| Rule | Compliance |
|------|------------|
| simulation remains authoritative | Encounter state is derived from simulation state |
| encounter state is serializable | All encounter state is plain dicts/lists |
| bounded logs/history | Log max 100 entries enforced |
| deterministic ordering | Participants sorted by (-initiative, actor_id) |
| no random turn selection | Turn index increments deterministically |
| encounter actions emit structured events | Log entries have round/text/type structure |

